data.description: Lovely one story, 2 bedroom, 2 bath, & 2 car deatached garage!! Selling as is! Plenty of green space all around! As soon as you enter this beauty you are greeted with a cozy family room! Beautiful kitchen with an open concept; lovely breakfast bar & breakfast area! Vaulted ceilings & a cozy fireplace in living area!! Third bedroom was expanded & combined with master bedroom. Charming master bedroom with appealing recessed lightning and en suite bath! Covered porch with access bar that can be used as an utility room, game room, study, etc! Minutes away from Baytown Airport, Stallworth Stadium, Local waterpark & Sports complexes! Easy access to I-10, & SH 146! Call now to schedule your own personal tour!
